Perhaps we could have a default value for this. For example, on auth I was doing:
 // Defaults
  private static final String TYPE = KeyStore.getDefaultType();
As this picks the runtime JDK default, for example on Java8 is JKS on java9 and up PKCS12 and maybe on other jdk's or runtimes started with custom security config it will be something else, e.g.: BKS
